descriptionHtml:

Description-
After the seige of the dark brotherhood sanctuary, only a few survived
now 2 months later... they return to skyrim
You can find your old buddies in the dawnstar sanctuary with 2 new members O_o

the newcomer is that typical dark elf you see running around with 2 daedric daggers (hint hint)

and the other is a pet wolf
you can find him in your room in the sanctuary
please enjoy!


bugs-
one of the members will constantly blabber that your tresspassing on strange occasions
the dark elf wont follow for some reason but is stuck as a follower (not sure how to fix that)
BUT i beleive that it is because of follower mods like UFO if he still acts glitchy then looks like you`ll have to use 
the console to fix him
